2. cs.DB (Databases) - The paper deals with generating SQL queries, which is closely related to database management systems and falls under the domain of CS.DB. 
3. cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) - The paper proposes a deep learning approach for text-to-SQL generation, which is a subfield of AI. 
4. cs.LG (Learning) - The paper proposes a neural architecture for text-to-SQL generation, which falls under the domain of machine learning and is a subfield of CS.LG. 
5. cs.IR (Information Retrieval) - The paper deals with generating SQL queries from natural language text, which is closely related to information retrieval and falls under the domain of CS.IR.
